      %p
        This is the NetHack Cross-Variant Summer Tournament. It runs annually during June.
      %p
        NetHack is a classic roguelike game. If you don't know what that is, try using
        a Google search.
      %p
        You can check out tournament rules from the
        %a{:href => "/rules"} rules page.
      %p
        There is a list of available trophies and competitions
        on the
        %a{:href => "/trophies"} trophies page.
      %p
        This tournament utilizes existing public NetHack servers, such as
        %a{:href => "http://alt.org/nethack"} nethack.alt.org.
        There are servers in both sides of the Atlantic for low latencies.
        People not living in Europe or Americas may find it harder to find a low
        latency server.
